item.title: About Me
item.description: I’m a software engineer, amateur astronomer & cricketer. On the internet, I’m f1rstmehul. I find coding in Go really, really fun 1. Distributed Systems and Compilers interest me the most. apart from being close to monitor, I like to explore the cosmos and play(and watch) cricket. I’m on, twitter, github and linkedin.
